div.p: If VA X != PA X at mov cr0, the fetch of the instruction at EIP+len will fault. Since no IDT is yet mapped, the CPU will Triple Fault.
Red = Critical Yellow = Intermediate Green = Stable

CR0 = 0x00000011 PG=0 PE=1
CR3 = 0x00000000 (no page dir)
EIP = 0x00101000 (phys addr)
ESP = 0x00090000 (phys addr)

Every load/store/fetch:
Virtual addr = Physical addr
No TLB lookups performed
No page table walks

0x00000000 BIOS / IVT / BDA (reserved)
0x00007C00 MBR/Stage1 remnant
0x00008000 Stage2 loader
0x00090000 Stack (grows )

0x00100000 Kernel .text / .rodata EIP
0x00104000 Kernel .data / .bss
0x00110000 boot_pd[1024] PAGE DIR
0x00111000 pt_identity[1024] table (low)
